### Is there an existing issue for this?

### Bug description

hi, Deeplabcut!
When the video of 2 mice is analyzed, there will be no data in the corresponding occluded or otherwise invisible body parts in the output CSV file. Curiously, most of the limbs were occluded during previous single-animal analysis, but there would still be corresponding csv data.
I think it may be related to this issue #1732
